<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="savings" id="idb07b370f-2930-11f1-a69d-9cbca84c43f0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Savings Provision</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For savings provision relating to payment or repayment of any bonus, incentive pay, special pay, or similar pay obligated to be paid before <date date="2006-04-01">Apr. 1, 2006</date>, under a provision of this section amended by <ref href="/us/pl/109/163/s687/b">section 687(b) of Pub. L. 109–163</ref>, see <ref href="/us/pl/109/163/s687/f">section 687(f) of Pub. L. 109–163</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s510">section 510 of Title 10</ref>, Armed Forces.</p>
</note>
